Adjust the path in the Makefile to be able to compile this in the POWHEGBOX-V2 framework.
You should install Herwig7.2 following the instructions in the directory HerwigInstallation (InstallationScript.sh).
In the directory HerwigInterface there are the remaining instructions to run Herwig7.2 using the events generated here.

An example of the POWHEG input card is provided in LQ3000-13TeV.